-- Francois Pinault Sees Sarkozy Losing Election, Le Monde Reports
-- B y   F a b i o   B e n e d e t t i - V a l e n t i n i
-- 2012-04-29T10:28:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-29/francois-pinault-sees-sarkozy-losing-election-le-monde-reports.html
Francois Pinault doesn’t see
President  Nicolas Sarkozy  winning re-election,  Le Monde 
reported, citing comments made by the French billionaire on
April 26.  “People close to him think that he may still win,”
Pinault said as he traveled to visit an art exhibition in
Colmar, eastern France, according to Le Monde. “He’s cooked!,”
he said about Sarkozy’s bid for re-election.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Fabio Benedetti-Valentini in Paris at 
